Tyrael's mind raced as he suspected what had happened to the ships. 
No, he wouldn't... Megatron wouldn't go back there...

Tyrael: Shadow Star, shoot those debris. The last thing we'd need now 
is a breach in the hull. Naga, get me the data you have gathered about 
this hole, whatever that is, on the big screen.
